<br>
Chain research for mages was just evil. Only class that had to do it too.<br>
<br>
I think they should reimplement reserach in different ways.<br>
<br>
To make the runes really useful you would need to allow them to stack.<br>
<br>
Heres are a few more<br>
<br>
Rune of Contortion: Shrinks a user who ducks :P<br>
<br>
Rune of Brilliance: Glows like a greater lightstone and adds +25% to your channeling skill. Consumed when a you channel through something message is displayed for you.<br>
<br>
Rune of Open Ways: +15% to lockpicking, consumed on a sucessfull lockpick.<br>
<br>
Rune of Scavenging: +15% to forage, consumed on a sucessefull forage.<br>
<br>
