The rune would be stackable.<br>
<br>
To Use the stack must be in the ammo slot.<br>
<br>
They will not refesh out of other inventory.<br>
<br>
But then again another Item.  Rune bag.  10 or 12 slot, tiny items only...  Runes in ammo will be refeshed like arrows in a quiver.<br>
<br>
The one I would imagine for pet channeling.  would raise the level of the pet by 2 or more levels.  Buff his atk by 50 or so.  add 200+ hp etc...  <br>
<br>
Since the runes are made up of something uncommon.  <br>
They will be hard enough to make  175+ skill, and the components uncommon enough, you would only want to use it when you knew you needed that extra power from a pet.  Not for everyday use.<br>
<br>
<br>
Look at it another way.  Runes could be the int casters form of potions.  However they are NOT right clickable like potions.  They are enhancers.<br>
<br>
