<br>
Since Focus Items are now *stat* increases and these runes work as focus items do, they would have to take up your range slot... something which would make them far less attractive.  <br>
<br>
The current game dynamics would have to be changed to allow this, which would introduce more bugs to be worked out and take much longer to implement.<br>
<br>
Unless I am totally mistaken and the Effects are being coded similar to how Coldstone gives you its effect...<br>
<br>
